[SN]TITLE[SN]
Former BBC producer and director Richard 'Dic' Lewis dies

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Former BBC Wales producer and director Richard Lewis has died.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Known by many as 'Dic', Mr Lewis worked on news programmes, documentaries, events and several dramas through the 1960s to 1980s.
He later joined Opus Television producing and directing several drama series and films for S4C, including the Bafta Cymru award winning Nel.
His other memorable works include Dylan, Nye, The Extremist, The Fasting Girl and Shadowlands.
